<P>
EXON TO SEEK THIRD TERM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By United Press International 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
LINCOLN, Neb. 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Sen. J. James Exon (D-Neb.) on Monday announced his bid for a third term. He 
was elected to the Senate in 1978. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
