ORANGE COUNTY -- TAXES; ORANGE COUNTY -- ELECTIONS -- 1990; SALES TAX -- ORANGE 
COUNTY; PRISONS -- ORANGE COUNTY; PRISONS -- OVERCROWDING; PROPOSITION 13 
(PROPERTY TAX); INITIATIVES -- ORANGE COUNTY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
